default2.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHolding the Chief Constable to account is a key statutory responsibility 
defaultand it is
default 
defaultimportant that both 
defaultI
default and the wider public can see how Surrey Police is performing against the Police &amp; Crime Plan and that the Force is rightly and properly subject to oversight, scrutiny and accountability to ensure it is operating efficiently and effectively. 
default&#xa0;default2.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultOne of my first acts as PCC was to do away with numerical targets for the police force – the first in the country to do so. The target culture has had a negative impact on British policing over the last 20 years.  
defaultTargets
default provide reassurance to politicians but they mean very little to the wider public. They can lead to perverse incentives towards policing activity that satisfies performance managers and no-one else. 
default&#xa0;
default2.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultNo targets does not mean no accountability however. I 
defaultopenly and constructively
default scrutinise the Chief Constable and the force
default. 
defaultI do not wish
default to take an adversarial approach
default,
default nor 
defaultdo I want
default senior officers and staff to be spending time in unnecessary meetings. In holding the Chief Constable to account, 
defaultI don’t seek to fetter 
defaulther
default 
defaultoperational independence or undermine her ability to direct and control the Force. 
defaultRather, I have sought to
default strike a balance between effective oversight and scrutiny and allowing the Chief Constable to deliver the ‘day job’.  
default&#xa0;
default2.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultCentral to my oversight activities are
default 
defaultbi-monthly 
defaultmanagement meetings.  
defaultT
defaulthes
defaulte 
defaultmanagement meetings 
defaultare webcast 
defaultlive 
defaultso that public, media, partners and police can see how I 
defaultam holding the 
defaultChief C
defaultonstable to account
default and what progress is being made
default.  
defaultI was the first, and until recently the only, PCC to webcast these meetings and bring about such a novel approach to transparency.  
defaultAgendas 
defaultare set in advance and papers publish
defaulted on my website for all to see.
default&#xa0;
default2.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn addition to this very public scrutiny, 
defaultand recognising that there is an equally important scrutiny role to be carried out on operationally or legally sensitive matters, 
defaultI meet privately with the Chief Constable at least every two weeks and more often as necessary
default.
default 
defaultMy staff also attend relevant Surrey Police meetings, such as their Crime Performance Board, to understand force performance in more detail. 
default&#xa0;
