default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI am also in the process of setting up a bi-mo
defaultnthly scrutiny panel.  
defaultAt this meeting I, my Deputy and Assistant PCCs will look at Surrey Police performance 
