default4.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMy view
default is that
default, post transfer,
default the Chief Constable should be responsible for the delivery of policing and I will hold her to account for the totality of that delivery.  My focus will remain on my strategic and 
defaultrepresentative
default role while the Chief 
defaultC
defaultonstable will focus on the delivery of operational policing with responsibility for the back office
default services that support this.  
defaultF
